All Classes

Class Description
Board
Board implements all Checker board related methods
BotLogics
BotLogics provides methods to retrieve legal move possibilities necessary for any programmed bot scripts
CheckersApp
CheckersApp provides central instances and functions of the Checkers app.
GameDesign
GameDesign provides additional game design related features for CheckersApp
GameLogics
GameLogics contains contains necessary logic methods to determine whether a capture move or capture is possible by Pieces / Kings.
Moves
Moves contains move and capture logics of Pieces of the CheckersApp
PDN
Portable Draughts Notation is the standard computer-processable format for recording checker games.
PDNNotRecognizedException
Thrown when given String PDN is not appropriate / recognized
Piece
Piece contains instances and methods related to individual pieces of CheckersApp
PieceNotRecognizedException
Thrown when there is not a declared piece for given button
RandomBot
RandomBot is a randomized Checkers bot making a random legal move on request
SidePanel
SidePanel implements the side bar of the CheckersApp
UnexpectedTileStatusException
Thrown when Tile status (empty / occupied) is unexpected
